name: Every hic et nunc whale (v2)
description: Our boat was stopped by the authorities, because it did not fulfill all the international waters regulations. Everything is now clarified and we are ready to leave the port towards v2 waters. We will inspect every H=N collect transaction and search for whale traces (mostly whale poop) to discover their latest incursions. This boat is powered by the TzKT API and it might not work in the future if the API calls change. Creator: Javier Gracia Carpio | @jagracar
